ernatorial election, 2012|2012]], [[Indiana gubernatorial election, 2016|2016]] (withdrew)}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Eric Holcomb]]}}\n\n{{s-bef|before=[[Paul Ryan]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]] [[List of United States Republican Party presidential tickets|nominee]] for Vice President of the United States|years=[[2016 United States presidential election|2016]], [[2020 United States presidential election|2020]] (presumptive)}}\n{{s-inc|recent}}\n\n{{s-off}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Mitch Daniels]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Governor of Indiana]]|years=2013\u20132017}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Eric Holcomb]]}}\n\n{{s-bef|before=[[Joe Biden]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Vice President of the United States]]|years=2017\u2013present}}\n{{s-inc}}\n\n{{s-prec|usa}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Donald Trump]]|as=[[President of the United States|President]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[United States order of precedence|Order of Precedence of the United States]]<br>''as [[Vice President of the United States]]''|years=}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Governor (United States)|Governor]] of state<br>in which event is held}}\n\n{{s-prec|us-pres}}\n{{s-bef|before=First}}\n{{s-ttl|title=1st in line<br>''as [[Vice President of the United States]]''|years=}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Nancy Pelosi]]|as=[[Speaker of the United States House of Representatives|Speaker of the U.S. House of Representatives]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n}}\n\n{{Navboxes\n|list =\n{{US Vice Presidents}}\n{{Trump cabinet}}\n{{Current U.S. Cabinet}}\n{{Pence Vice Presidential staff}}\n{{US Presidential Line of Succession}}\n{{US Senate leaders}}\n{{Governors of Indiana}}\n{{US House Republican Conference Chairs}}\n{{IndianaUSRepresentatives}}\n{{Republican Party (United States)}}\n{{2016 United States presidential election}}\n{{US Order of Precedence}}\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pence, Mike}}\n[[Category:Mike Pence|*]]\n[[Category:1959 births]]\n[[Category:2016 United States vice-presidential candidates]]\n[[Category:20th-century American politicians]]